4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with the skills needed for a tech career. Over 18 weeks, participants will learn essential technologies such as JavaScript and Python, focusing on web development, algorithm scripting, and app creation. No prior coding experience is necessary, and classes are available in both English and Spanish. The program features hands-on projects, a class size ratio of 1 instructor per 7 students, and three classes per week. Upon completion, students receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop